# {{kb_name}}

A personal knowledge base built from Twitter/X bookmarks. Bookmarks are synced from a logged-in browser session, clustered into topic batches by a deterministic script using a Claude-derived map, and synthesized into wiki pages. This file is the operational contract between the user and Claude.

> This KB is managed by the **twitter-wiki** Claude Code skill. The skill provides slash commands (`/kb-sync`, `/kb-ingest`, `/kb-recluster`, `/kb-query`, `/kb-lint`, `/kb-status`) and the synthesis logic. See `~/.claude/skills/twitter-wiki/SKILL.md` for the full operational spec.

Created: {{created_date}}

