## Core operations

These are run by the user via slash commands and orchestrated by the **twitter-wiki** skill. See the skill's SKILL.md for the full workflows.

| Command | Effect |
|---|---|
| `/kb-sync` | Pulls new bookmarks from the user's browser session into `raw/bookmarks.jsonl` |
| `/kb-ingest` | First run bootstraps `cluster-map.json`. Then preprocesses into batches, then synthesizes/updates wiki pages |
| `/kb-recluster [hint]` | Re-derives the topic map and reconciles affected wiki pages |
| `/kb-query <q>` | Answers a question grounded in the wiki, optionally saves the answer under `wiki/queries/` |
| `/kb-lint` | Static + semantic health check, fixes what's auto-fixable |
| `/kb-status` | Sync + ingest stats |

